senselogic.sitevision.api.webresource

Interface LinkTarget


  • public interface LinkTarget
    A temporary representation of a link target.

    An instance of this interface is typically used in LinkPageUtil when setting the target of a LinkPage.

    An instance of the Sitevision class implementing this interface can be obtained via LinkTargetBuilder.build(). See LinkTargetBuilder for how to obtain an instance of the LinkTargetBuilder interface.
